cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is most likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation systems and language modeling objectives. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves training a model to predict subsets of target words. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves developing a more efficient and accurate translation model. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks for machine translation. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves generating text, which is a form of image-to-text translation.
